and look in at your son.

358
00:22:22,235 --> 00:22:24,758
- It's just down the hall.
- Thank you.

359
00:22:31,235 --> 00:22:33,109
A baby boy.

360
00:22:37,048 --> 00:22:39,913
- Congratulations.
- You're all right, Don.

361
00:22:42,891 --> 00:22:45,071
