369
00:23:10,488 --> 00:23:11,938
We don't deserve it.

370
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:16,978
This is a fresh start.

371
00:23:18,399 --> 00:23:20,572
I don't know who's up there,

372
00:23:21,468 --> 00:23:23,318
so I'm saying this to you.

373
00:23:24,363 --> 00:23:25,813
I'm gonna be better.

374
00:23:26,985 --> 00:23:28,572
