382
00:24:45,805 --> 00:24:46,605
Daddy?

383
00:24:48,365 --> 00:24:50,483
- Who are you?
- It's me.

384
00:24:53,235 --> 00:24:54,585
I don't know you.

385
00:24:55,795 --> 00:24:57,612
It's me... Elizabeth.

386
00:25:03,111 --> 00:25:04,361
You do know me.

387
00:25:07,311 --> 00:25:08,631
Okay, so it's me.

388
00:25:09,057 --> 00:25:12,135
- What are you doing here?
- I had to go away.

389
00:25:12,987 --> 00:25:15,609
- Well, don't you Miss me?
- Of course.

390
00:25:17,173 --> 00:25:18,173
Listen.

391
00:25:19,596 --> 00:25:21,546
