393
00:25:30,174 --> 00:25:31,424
Ask your mother.

394
00:25:32,422 --> 00:25:33,772
Tell her, Ruthie.

395
00:25:36,051 --> 00:25:38,411
Shut your mouth.
You'll catch flies.

396
00:25:45,124 --> 00:25:47,049
I left my lunch pail on the bus

397
00:25:47,369 --> 00:25:48,838
